@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN
@measurementId = measurement_1

### 연령대 기반 활동 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities?ageGroup=PRESCHOOL&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 체력 요소 기반 활동 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities?fitnessElement=CARDIO,POWER&ageGroup=PRESCHOOL&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 측정 약점 기반 활동 추천
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities?measurementId={{measurementId}}&ageGroup=PRESCHOOL&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
